    • uniol.apt.adt.extension.Extensible
      • uniol.apt.adt.subgraph.SubEdge<G,E,N>
  • Type Parameters:
    G - The type of the graph of which we are a subgraph.
    E - The type of edges of the graph of which we are a subgraph.
    N - The type of nodes of the graph of which we are a subgraph.
